query: SELECT dt.id, dt.name, dt.category FROM document_types dt WHERE dt.id NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT documentTypeId FROM documents WHERE documentTypeId IS NOT NULL) AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM document_types dt2 WHERE dt2.name = dt.name AND dt2.category = dt.category AND dt2.id < dt.id) ORDER BY dt.name;
